Date: Fri 31 Jul 2020 20:00 EDT
Source: CDC [edited]
https://www.cdc.gov/salmonella/newport-07-20/index.html


Outbreak of _Salmonella_ Newport infections linked to red onions
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Since the last update on 24 Jul 2020, an additional 184 ill people have been reported in this outbreak, including 37 from 11 new states: Alaska, Colorado, Indiana, Kansas, Kentucky, Maryland, Nevada, New York, Pennsylvania, South Carolina, Texas.

As of 29 Jul 2020, a total of 396 people infected with the outbreak strain of _Salmonella [enterica_ serotype] Newport have been reported from 34 states.

